#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:4
msgid "Smooth Modifier"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:6
msgid ""
"The *Smooth Modifier* smooths a mesh by flattening the angles between "
"adjacent faces in it, just like :menuselection:`Specials --> Smooth` in "
"Edit Mode. It smooths without subdividing the mesh - the number of "
"vertices remains the same."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:12
msgid "Smooth modifier applied to a subdivided cube."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:14
msgid ""
"This modifier is not limited to smoothing, though. Its control factor can"
" be configured outside the (0.0 to 1.0) range (including negative "
"values), which can result in interesting deformations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:20
msgid "Options"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:22
msgid "X, Y, Z"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:23
msgid ""
"Toggle buttons to enable/disable the modifier in the X, Y and/or Z axes "
"directions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:26
msgid "Factor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:25
msgid ""
"The factor to control the smoothing amount. Higher values will increase "
"the effect. Values outside this range (above 1.0 or below 0.0) distort "
"the mesh."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:29
msgid "Repeat"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:29
msgid ""
"The number of smoothing iterations, equivalent to executing the smooth "
"tool multiple times."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:34
msgid "Vertex Group"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:32
msgid ""
"A vertex group name, to restrict the effect to the vertices in it only. "
"This allows for selective, real-time smoothing, by painting vertex "
"weights."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:37
msgid "Algorithm"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:39
msgid ""
"The calculation done by the Smooth Modifier is a simple and logical one, "
"and can be thought of as the geometric equivalent of blurring images."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/smooth.rst:42
msgid ""
"Each new vertex position is simply the average position of surrounding "
"vertices (the vertices connected to the same edge as it)."
msgstr ""

